<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This standard is prescribed in accordance with the provisions of Article 17 of the Act Governing Food Safety and Sanitation (herein referred to as "this Act").]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The scopes of this standard include food microorganisms and their toxins or metabolites, but do not include fungi and mycotoxins.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The limits for food microorganisms and their toxins or metabolites shall meet the requirements in the table in Annex.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[Non-compliant under the jurisdiction of subparagraphs 4 of paragraph 1 of Article 15 of this Act and Article 6 of Rules for the Implementation of this Act, shall be sanctioned in accordance with violating Article 15 of this Act.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This standard shall be implemented from July 1, 2021.]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
